uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.owl

Class OModelCopier

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.owl.OModelCreator
      • uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.owl.OModelCopier

  • public class OModelCopier
extends OModelCreator
    Responsible for copying the model represented by an OModel object, possibly with a different type of reasoner and/or updated reasoning-type. Copied models will contain only copies of the contents of the model ontology. Any contents of the instance ontology will not be copied.
